# MatchMate 👥💍

**MatchMate** is a matrimonial-style Android app that allows users to swipe through match cards, accept or decline matches, and persist those decisions even offline.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🧠 MVVM architecture using ViewModel, LiveData, Repository
- 🌐 Fetch user profiles from [randomuser.me](https://randomuser.me/)
- 📦 Persist match decisions using Room DB (offline support)
- 🖼️ Load profile pictures using Glide
- 🔄 Retrofit for API integration
- 📱 Clean UI with RecyclerView + ViewBinding

---

## 🏗️ Tech Stack

| Layer          | Tool/Library                          |
|----------------|---------------------------------------|
| UI             | RecyclerView, ConstraintLayout, ViewBinding |
| Network        | Retrofit + Gson                       |
| Image Loading  | Glide                                 |
| Local DB       | Room                                  |
| Architecture   | MVVM (ViewModel, Repository, LiveData)|
| Language       | Kotlin                                |

