## 🛠️ How to Run

1. Clone this repo:
    ```bash
    git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/MatchMate.git
    ```

2. Open in **Android Studio**
3. Ensure the following are enabled in `build.gradle.kts`:
    ```kotlin
    buildFeatures {
        viewBinding = true
    }
    ```

4. Add this permission in your `AndroidManifest.xml`:
    ```xml
    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.INTERNET" />
    ```

5. Run the app on an emulator or device with internet access

